ZISALOKHE zibuye njalo izigameko zishaqisayo emabandleni kuleli ngaphezu kwemizamo kahulumeni nezinhlangano ezizimele yokuzinqanda. Esigamekweni sakamuva kubonakale uMfundisi uLight Monyeki edla umuthi wamagundane iRattex nebandla lakhe elitshela ukuthi ukufa akunasabelo kubona kuleli Sonto elidlule. Lo mfundisi kuthiwa ubexuba iRattex namanzi ephuzisa abazalwane ethi uyabelapha. Ekhasini lebandla iGrace Living Hope Ministries kuFacebook, uvele ephuzisa amalungu ebandla iRattex nokuyinto ayibize ngokukhombisa amandla okholo.&nbsp; Kuthiwa lo mfundisi watshela amalungu ebandla ukuthi uma abafana abadla nyaope(iwhoonga) exutshwe neRattex iminyaka edlule kwengu-8 bephile, nabo ayikho into engabavimba futhi ukufa akunasabelo phezu kwabo. Ngokombhalo okuFacebook kuthiwa umfundisi wanele waqhabula kule ngxube yeRattex, amalungu ebandla eza egijima phambili efuna ukuphuza nawo.&nbsp; .&nbsp; ISITHOMBE: Facebook &nbsp;INyaope(Whonga) kuthiwa yakhiwe ngensangu,umuthi wokubulala amagundane namakhemikhali iChlorine ne-Ammonia. Amalungu aleli bandla awatholakalanga ukuphawula kwabezindaba. UMonyeki akayena umfundisi wokuqala ukuphuzisa abazalwane izinto ezingadliwa eziyingozi. Umfundisi waseLimpopo uLethebo Rabalago washaqa abantu abaninigi efutha abantu ngeDoom nokwaholela ekutheni ethole incwadi eyisivimbelo senkantolo.&nbsp; &nbsp;INyaope(Whonga) kuthiwa yakhiwe ngensangu,umuthi wokubulala amagundane namakhemikhali iChlorine ne-Ammonia. Amalungu aleli bandla awatholakalanga ukuphawula kwabezindaba. UMonyeki akayena umfundisi wokuqala ukuphuzisa abazalwane izinto ezingadliwa eziyingozi. Umfundisi waseLimpopo uLethebo Rabalago washaqa abantu abaninigi efutha abantu ngeDoom nokwaholela ekutheni ethole incwadi eyisivimbelo senkantolo.&nbsp;